                            an interesting read and while I may agree with the conclusion I think I may not agree with some of the supporting evidence.
Pounds vs Dollars
While financially I doubt there‚Äôs much difference. I do think CONVERSION to my local currency would be valuable. (BundleStars ‚Äì http://www.bundlestars.com/ ) does this and it‚Äôs in valuable. 
While i understand it‚Äôs hard to judge I don‚Äôt see any thought given to the quality of the two products vs demand. Is it possible that the IGG didn‚Äôt do as well because the KS product was better? Probably not but I note the absence of that being factored out.
You do have KickTraq on the list twice for exactly the same reason. I get it KickTraq is on KS and not IGG. I‚Äôve always found judging phones because of an app one had that the other doesn‚Äôt to be odd. The fact that one phone has this app and my phone doesn‚Äôt. Doesn‚Äôt make it better. It makes the APP selection better and that might be a factor in making the decision but my phone still has a larger screen a faster processor and a smoother OS.
That said it sounds like KickTraq is a useful tool to the platform. 
&gt;Vastly smaller audience to sell too
this like KickTraq is imo slightly wrong criteria to judge. Ordinarily I might say the audience has nothing to do with how good the website is but in a crowd funding site that‚Äôs not exactly true. 
Still, that said I think we‚Äôre mixing up aspects of the site with feasibility of using it. There‚Äôs plenty IGG can do to fix things like pledge alterations and mass emails and such. There‚Äôs nothing they can do directly to inflate their user base. That again is like saying the iPhone is a better phone because more people use it. The two are related but not causally.

                        
                    
                    


                
                
                
                        
                        
							
                        
                    
                    
                    
                        
                            
